    "DisplayTitle": "Bounty Assignment: [TargetName] (HRT)",
    "Description": "Hey, \n\nGot a contract for you that requires a bit more tactics than usual. A high-level criminal by the name ~mission(TargetName) is hiding with a large contingent of outlaws at ~mission(Location|Address). \n\nOur intel suggests that ~mission(TargetName|Last)\u2019s forces most likely will act as defensive line in order to protect their boss. My best guess is that you will have to deal with them before you gain access to ~mission(TargetName|Last).\n\nThat said, I don\u2019t want you shooting indiscriminately. Sometimes these outlaws keep civilians around and they should be treated like non-combatants.\n\nBest of luck,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hey, \n\nGot a contract for you that requires a bit more tactics than usual. A high-level criminal by the name [TargetName] is hiding with a large contingent of outlaws at [Location|Address]. \n\nOur intel suggests that [TargetName|Last]\u2019s forces most likely will act as defensive line in order to protect their boss. My best guess is that you will have to deal with them before you gain access to [TargetName|Last].\n\nThat said, I don\u2019t want you shooting indiscriminately. Sometimes these outlaws keep civilians around and they should be treated like non-combatants.\n\nBest of luck,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
